
ringserver - Generic packet ring buffer

See the ringserver.1 man page in the 'doc' directory
for a more detailed description.

-- Building/Installing --

In most environments a simple 'make' will build the program.

The CC and CFLAGS environment variables can be used to configure
the build parameters.

SunOS/Solaris:
 
In order to compile under Solaris the 'src/Makefile' needs to be edited.
See the Makefile for instructions.

For further installation simply copy the resulting binary and man page
(in the 'doc' directory) to appropriate system directories.

